        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "Dick came up and kissed Esmond on both cheeks, imparting a strong perfume of burnt sack along with his caress to the young man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "I protest I should have known thee anywhere.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "I always hated that fellow Mohun.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "I would wager 'twas a woman.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "\"'twas a quarrel about play-on my word, about play,\" Harry said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "It was the softest hand that struck him, the gentlest and most compassionate nature that persecuted him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000011_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000011_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "\"I would as lief,\" he said, \"have pleaded guilty to the murder, and have suffered for it like any other felon, as have to endure the torture to which my mistress subjects me.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "\"And I think I spoke well, my poor boy,\" says mr Steele; \"for who would not speak well in such a cause, and before so beautiful a judge?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "But these young gentlemen went off to the garden; I could see them from the window tilting at each other with poles in a mimic tournament (grief touches the young but lightly, and I remember that I beat a drum at the coffin of my own father).",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000013_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000013_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "I think I never saw such a beautiful violet as that of her eyes, Harry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "My lord might have been here but for that; my home might be happy; my poor boy have a father.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000015_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000015_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "It was what you gentlemen call gallantry came into my home, and drove my husband on to the cruel sword that killed him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000015_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000015_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "You should not speak the word to a Christian woman, sir, a poor widowed mother of orphans, whose home was happy until the world came into it-the wicked godless world, that takes the blood of the innocent, and lets the guilty go free.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "\"As the afflicted lady spoke in this strain, sir,\" mr Steele continued, \"it seemed as if indignation moved her, even more than grief. 'Compensation!' she went on passionately, her cheeks and eyes kindling; 'what compensation does your world give the widow for her husband, and the children for the murderer of their father?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "The wretch who did the deed has not even a punishment.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "Conscience! what conscience has he, who can enter the house of a friend, whisper falsehood and insult to a woman that never harmed him, and stab the kind heart that trusted him?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000016_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000016_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "That day, my Lord-my Lord Murderer-(I will never name him)--was let loose, a woman was executed at Tyburn for stealing in a shop.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000016_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000016_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "But a man may rob another of his life, or a lady of her honor, and shall pay no penalty!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000016_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000016_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "I take my child, run to the throne, and on my knees ask for justice, and the King refuses me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "\"'Are you come from HIM?' asked the lady (so mr Steele went on) rising up with a great severity and stateliness.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "'I thought you had come from the Princess.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "I saw mr Esmond in his prison, and bade him farewell.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "He brought misery into my house.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "\"'Do I blame him to you, sir?' asked the widow.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "It may be, in years hence, when-when our knees and our tears and our contrition have changed our sinful hearts, sir, and wrought our pardon, we may meet again-but not now.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000020_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000020_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "After what has passed, I could not bear to see him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000022_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000022_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "'mr Esmond will find other-other friends.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000022_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000022_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "Whilst I live in it, after the horrid horrid deed which has passed, Castlewood must never be a home to him-never.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "\"Here the fair Beatrix entered from the river, with her cheeks flushing with health, and looking only the more lovely and fresh for the mourning habiliments which she wore.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "\"'Beatrix, this is mr Steele, gentleman usher to the Prince's Highness. When does your new comedy appear, mr Steele?' I hope thou wilt be out of prison for the first night, Harry.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-895_136366_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/895/136366/895_136366_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-895",
        "content": "Our rooms were the three in the gate over Newgate-on the second story looking up Newgate Street towards Cheapside and Paul's Church.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    }
